Uche Lilian Ekwunife (née Ogudebe amụrụ ya n' ụbọchị iri na abụọ n' ọnwa nke mbụ ,Jenụwarị 1970), bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Naijiria, na onye otu Sị́neti nke itolu nke Naijiria na-anọchite anya ndị Anambra Central Senatorial District nke Anambra Steeti ma a maara ya dị ka otu n'ime ndị sineti nwanyị kachasị arụsi ọrụ ike n'ụlọ.
Ekwunife nwere ọrụ na ụlọ akụ ebe ọ ghọrọ onye njikwa mpaghara
Ọ lụrụ onye ọchụnta ego si Nri [circular reference] obodo Anaocha LGA. Ya na Chief Larry Ekwunife nwere ụmụ.
